<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s calm thoughts -->
  <BondedThoughtCalm.stages.s_calm_thoughts.label>{WEAPON}的寧靜</BondedThoughtCalm.stages.s_calm_thoughts.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}, my bonded weapon, is whispering calming thoughts to me. -->
  <BondedThoughtCalm.stages.s_calm_thoughts.description>我的綁定武器{WEAPON}，正對我耳語寧靜的秘語。</BondedThoughtCalm.stages.s_calm_thoughts.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s kind thoughts -->
  <BondedThoughtKind.stages.s_kind_thoughts.label>{WEAPON}的溫柔</BondedThoughtKind.stages.s_kind_thoughts.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}, my bonded weapon, is whispering kind thoughts to me. -->
  <BondedThoughtKind.stages.s_kind_thoughts.description>我的綁定武器{WEAPON}，正向我傳遞幸福。</BondedThoughtKind.stages.s_kind_thoughts.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s muttering -->
  <BondedThoughtMuttering.stages.s_muttering.label>{WEAPON}的喃喃自語</BondedThoughtMuttering.stages.s_muttering.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}, my bonded weapon, is muttering in my head. It's hard to ignore sometimes. -->
  <BondedThoughtMuttering.stages.s_muttering.description>我的綁定武器{WEAPON}，正在我腦海裡喋喋不休，這個真讓人很難忽視。</BondedThoughtMuttering.stages.s_muttering.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s wailing -->
  <BondedThoughtWailing.stages.s_wailing.label>{WEAPON}的哀嚎</BondedThoughtWailing.stages.s_wailing.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}, my bonded weapon, is wailing madly in my head. I wish I could ignore it. -->
  <BondedThoughtWailing.stages.s_wailing.description>我的綁定武器{WEAPON}，正在我腦海裡瘋狂嚎叫，真希望我能忽略掉它。</BondedThoughtWailing.stages.s_wailing.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s jealousy -->
  <JealousRage.stages.s_jealousy.label>{WEAPON}的忌妒</JealousRage.stages.s_jealousy.label>
  <!-- EN: My bonded weapon {WEAPON} is jealous I am using another weapon. I can feel the rage it is screaming into my head. -->
  <JealousRage.stages.s_jealousy.description>我的綁定武器{WEAPON}對於我使用另外的武器感到嫉妒，我能感受到它在我腦海中憤怒的尖叫。</JealousRage.stages.s_jealousy.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s kill thirst -->
  <KillThirst.stages.s_kill_thirst.label>{WEAPON}的殺戮渴望</KillThirst.stages.s_kill_thirst.label>
  <!-- EN: My bonded weapon {WEAPON} is angry it has gone so long without killing. I can feel its rage. -->
  <KillThirst.stages.s_kill_thirst.description>我的綁定武器{WEAPON}太久沒有沾血了，它十分生氣，我能感受到它的憤怒。</KillThirst.stages.s_kill_thirst.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s kill sorrow -->
  <OnKill_BadThought.stages.s_kill_sorrow.label>{WEAPON}的殺生厭棄</OnKill_BadThought.stages.s_kill_sorrow.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s sorrow over its kill is affecting my mind as well. -->
  <OnKill_BadThought.stages.s_kill_sorrow.description>{WEAPON}對因它而生的殺戮感到悲傷，這同樣也影響到了我。</OnKill_BadThought.stages.s_kill_sorrow.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s kill happiness -->
  <OnKill_GoodThought.stages.s_kill_happiness.label>{WEAPON}的殺戮歡愉</OnKill_GoodThought.stages.s_kill_happiness.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON} was overjoyed with its kill, and I feel some of that too. -->
  <OnKill_GoodThought.stages.s_kill_happiness.description>{WEAPON}對它的殺戮欣喜若狂，我也獲得了相同的感受。</OnKill_GoodThought.stages.s_kill_happiness.description>
  
</LanguageData>